itunes:summary: Thaddeus Brown was a founding member of The Smoking Tire, the DP of /TUNED and /BIG MUSCLE. It was his brain that thought up the crazy idea that became our "All Cars go to Heaven" series. He now lives in Dubai, working as a creative director for various ad campaigns.
